		scsim19 			Moose
		EE	adstoch	G1	GB	EE	adstoch	G1	RK5
kholodenko.g 	12	18	6	8	18	10	0.6	0.9
1e5 sec                                          

acc4_1e-21.g 	11	21	190	75	25	27	85	75
1000 sec

nonscaf_syn6	13	22	160	41	28	28	36	65
100 sec

